title: FIFA keeps Feb. 26 election date; Platini status uncertain
text:
> Sports FIFA keeps Feb. 26 election date; Platini status uncertain Media representatives wait outside of the FIFA headquarters in Zurich, Switzerland as board members arrive at the FIFA headquarters in Zurich, Switzerland, Tuesday Oct. 20, 2015. A FIFA Executive Committee meeting will take place at the Home of FIFA in Zurich. (Walter Bieri/Keystone via AP) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
